    "title": "Lead Revenue Manager at Kumarakom Lake Resort Holdings Services",
    "description": "If you're a passionate Revenue Manager with drive and ambition, Kumarakom Lake Resort Holdings Services in Varanasi is the place for you. We're growing fast and need talented people to grow with us.\n\nAbout Kumarakom Lake Resort Holdings Services:\nKumarakom Lake Resort Holdings Services is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Ensure compliance with FSSAI, health, and safety regulations\n• Assist in menu planning, costing, and food festival coordination\n• Monitor F&B service quality and maintain hygiene standards\n• Train and supervise front-line staff on service standards\n• Plan and execute banquets, events, and MICE functions\n• Manage procurement of hotel supplies and control operating costs\n• Handle guest complaints and resolve issues promptly\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBA from a recognized university\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Housekeeping Standards\n• Proficiency in OTA Management\n• Proficiency in Revenue Management\n• Proficiency in Yield Management\n• Proficiency in PMS Systems\n• Proficiency in Travel Management\n• Proficiency in Event Management\n• Proficiency in Front Office\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Referral bonus program\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Varanasi, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Kumarakom Lake Resort Holdings Services!",
